info.author: Richard Boltze
info.name: sphere-base
info.summary: The library was created to be used as a building block for applications were informationshould appear on the surface of a sphere. It allows for creating spheres with nodesand edges that can be dragged on its surface. Nodes and edges can be placed and removed from the sphere surface.
